{
  "stem": "17001.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 56.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If this hardened up man who goes through the woods and everything, and they look at us and they start to cry, then we must be a pathetic-- pathetic sight.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was Elizabeth with you also?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were all four of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened is after that, they had asked-- the partisans had asked us that being that it was May the 5th, that we should-- whoever feel strong enough to carry a gun, that we should go with them because many of the German soldiers are hiding in the forest, that we should able to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So naturally, I wasn't in that shape, and I wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meantime, I was looking for this woman who stole the blanket from us in-- in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went with them, because I told her that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, you are such a bastard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a Jewish mother, you have a child, and you made us get this beating.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, after the war, I will kill you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I'm not just saying it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will kill you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you know, she was the first one to go with the partisans, and she disappeared.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never seen her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Stubenalteste and all the big horses who were stealing us blind with the bread and all that, they all went with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were left without any supervision.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would say we were left about 200, 220, something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there about a month, until we started to get to our feet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the thing is that when they liberated us, this Yugoslavs, some of the sick girls who were in one of this little room, one of them I befriended already in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
